    <item>
      <title>Big Lots 推迟与 Nexus 收购要约相关的关键听证会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/big-lots-delays-key-hearing-connected-to-nexus-takeover-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Big Lots Inc. 推迟了一场重要的法庭听证会，该听证会将决定私募股权公司 Nexus Capital Management 是否应该被列为潜在破产拍卖的领衔竞标者，此前该公司本周早些时候表示，该公司仍需与公司贷方就约 7.5 亿美元的融资达成协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/big-lots-delays-key-hearing-connected-to-nexus-takeover-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 16:14:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
